Anh - Anh
gook
gook1[gu:k, gʊk]
■ noun N. Amer. informal, offensive a foreigner, especially a person of SE Asian descent.
Origin
1930s: of unknown origin.
————————
gook2[gu:k, gʊk]
■ noun informal a sloppy wet or viscous substance.
Origin
1970s: var. of guck.
